ial interest in view of the recent detection of\nblack-hole mergers by LIGO. The possibility of Planck relics is also intriguing\nbut virtually untestable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Jul 2016 19:53:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2016 19:52:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2016 15:36:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 22 Mar 2017 17:29:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-23"}
