her reason of why\nQuasi-Periodic Oscillations should be observed in black hole candidates which\nare accreting low angular momentum transonic flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jul 2016 04:44:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-07"}
